comments: Anthony (POR) places an arm to Green's (LAC) front at the start of his drive but the contact is marginal as he releases.
Mann (LAC) briefly places his hand to Nurkic's (POR) shoulder but does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
McCollum (POR) wraps Shamet (LAC) around the waist during the inbound.  After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of an away from the play foul is confirmed.
Shamet (LAC) places an arm against Nurkic (POR) but the contact is marginal as he releases.
McCollum (POR) legally contest Shamet's (LAC) driving shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) briefly grasps Patterson's (LAC) arm in the post and disengages.
McCollum (POR) makes contact to Patterson's (LAC) body that affects his play at the basket.
Anthony (POR) engages and disengages with Patterson (LAC) during the screen.
Green (LAC) makes contact with Nurkic's (POR) arm during the rip-through that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Nurkic (POR) sets the screen on Shamet (LAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Lillard (POR) splits his feet prior to the start of his dribble.
Green (LAC) places his forearm to Lillard's (POR) side but removes it as he gathers.
Lillard (POR) briefly places his arm to Patterson's (LAC) front but the contact is marginal.
Nurkic (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during Mann's (LAC) drive.
Nurkic's (POR) leg is extended when he makes foot to foot contact with Mann (LAC) that trips him and affects his balance.
McGruder (LAC) initiates contact to Lillard's (POR) body and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) grabs Green's (LAC) jersey and affects his ability to retrieve the loose ball.
Collins (POR) makes marginal contact with Green (LAC) during rebounding.
Lillard (POR) commits a take foul on Shamet (LAC).
